==Translingual==

===Symbol===
'''M'''

# [[mega-]]
# {{astronomy}}: [[Messier number]]. Objects in [[w:Charles Messier|Charles Messier's]] catalog of ''Nebulae and Star Clusters'' in 1774 are numbered, and the letter '''M''' (for Messier) is prepended to these numbers, as in [[M31]] (the Andromeda Galaxy) or [[M13]] (the globular cluster in Hercules).

----
